<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
	  xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
	  xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal">
	<head>
		<meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
		<title>Welcome To NextThought</title>
		<style metal:use-macro="macro:style">
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div metal:use-macro="macro:header">
		</div>

		<p>Dear <span tal:content="options/informal_username" class="realname tterm">John</span>,</p>

		<p>
			Thank you for signing up for
			&ldquo;<span tal:content="options/course/Title |
			default">Gateway to College Learning</span>,&rdquo; an
			open version of the popular course taken by incoming
			freshmen during their first semester at the University of
			Oklahoma. You are welcome to join us to experience the
			lectures and discussions available
			through <a href="https://janux.ou.edu"
			title="Janux">Janux</a>.
		</p>

		<p>
			The course begins August 18, 2014. Feel free to spread the
			word about the course by forwarding this email or sharing
			about it through social media. If you are an incoming OU
			student, you have the option to enroll in the
			&ldquo;<span tal:content="options/course/Title |
			default">Gateway to College Learning</span>,&rdquo; course
			for credit. Enroll at <a href="https://ozone.ou.edu"
			alt="ozone">ozone.ou.edu</a> with the corresponding course
			number: UCOL 1002.
		</p>

		<p>
			I look forward to seeing you in our community,
			<br />
			<br />
			<span  tal:content="structure options/instructors_html_signature">
				Lillian Miller<br />
				Director of Freshman Programs<br />
				University of Oklahoma<br />
			</span>
		</p>

		<div id="logo-bar nti">
			<img src="http://d2ixlfeu83tci.cloudfront.net/images/email_logo.png" width="177" height="25" alt="NextThought Logo" />
		</div>

		<p class="footer" style="font-size: smaller">
			If you feel this email was sent in error, or this account was created
			without your consent, you may email
			<a href="mailto:support@nextthought.com">support@nextthought.com</a>.
		</p>


	</body>
</html>
